name: license
description: license that comes with the data

name: carob_contributor
description: name(s) of contributers of this script

name: data_type
description: what kind of data is this (e.g. experiment, survey, compilation)

name: publication
description: the doi of the associated publication (if any)

name: data_organization
description: organizational home(s) of the data providers

name: project
description: project that this dataset belongs to (if any)

name: carob_date
description: date of first contribution to Carob

name: last_modified
description: date of last significant revision of the script

name: modified_by
description: name(s) of contributers who made significant changes to the script

name: notes
description: notes about data quality issues in the dataset

name: design
description: short description of the experimental or survey design

name: completion
description: the percentage of relevant variables that have been standardized
